```plantuml
@startuml Elkinmt19_feature-hero-ml

actor User

participant "User Application" as UserApp
participant "Feature Store" as FeatureStore
participant "Feast" as Feast
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "Parquet" as Parquet
participant "ETL Pipeline" as ETL
participant "Docker Compose" as DockerCompose

User -> UserApp: Request Features
UserApp -> FeatureStore: Query Features
FeatureStore -> Feast: Retrieve Feature Definition
Feast -> Redis: Fetch Online Features
Redis --> Feast: Return Features
Feast -> Parquet: Fetch Offline Features
Parquet --> Feast: Return Features
Feast --> FeatureStore: Aggregated Features
FeatureStore --> UserApp: Return Features
UserApp --> User: Display Features

UserApp -> ETL: Trigger Data Pipeline
ETL -> FeatureStore: Ingest Data
ETL -> Feast: Update Feature Views
Feast -> Parquet: Store Batch Data
Parquet --> Feast: Confirm Storage

DockerCompose -> DockerCompose: Start Services
DockerCompose -> Redis: Initialize
DockerCompose -> Parquet: Initialize
DockerCompose -> FeatureStore: Initialize

@enduml
```